<h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>



<p><strong>How do I format my ingredient list?</strong></p>



<p>Simply type or paste your ingredient list into the text area with each i=
ngredient on its own line. The format should include quantity and measureme=
nt (like =E2=80=9C2 cups flour=E2=80=9D or =E2=80=9C1 tablespoon olive oil=
=E2=80=9D). Our smart parser automatically handles various measurement form=
ats.</p>



<p><strong>What=E2=80=99s the difference between multiplier and portion con=
version?</strong></p>



<p>Multiplier conversion scales by a specific factor (like doubling with 2x=
